    <item>
      <title>Console: new Domains management interface</title>
      <link>https://stagingv6.cleverapps.io/developers/changelog/2024-07-26-domains-console-update/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://stagingv6.cleverapps.io/developers/changelog/2024-07-26-domains-console-update/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;We&amp;rsquo;ve upgraded the applications&amp;rsquo; Domains page in the Console. It&amp;rsquo;s now more clear, complete and easy to use. We designed it to highlight some of our underrated features such as &lt;a href=&#34;https://stagingv6.cleverapps.io/developers/doc/administrate/domain-names/#path-routing&#34; &gt;path routing&lt;/a&gt;. You also now have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A unique form to add a custom domain or a test domain (&lt;code&gt;cleverapps.io&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A unique list of test and custom domains&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A direct link to add your own certificate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clearer error messages/warnings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clearer instructions about DNS configuration and IP lists&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Better accessibility, responsiveness, internationalization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Console: new logs interface is now used by default</title>
      <link>https://stagingv6.cleverapps.io/developers/changelog/2024-07-17-new-logs-default/</link>
