        &lt;p&gt;New logs interface is available in the Console in public beta &lt;a href=&#34;https://stagingv6.cleverapps.io/developers/changelog/2024-04-15-new-logs-interface-public-beta/&#34; &gt;for some months&lt;/a&gt;, and we already &lt;a href=&#34;https://stagingv6.cleverapps.io/developers/changelog/2024-06-21-better-new-logs/&#34; &gt;enhanced it&lt;/a&gt;. We&amp;rsquo;re now confident enough to use it by default. You can still disable it. If you have any question or feedback, use our &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/CleverCloud/Community/discussions/categories/new-logs-interface&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;GitHub Community space&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
