      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://stagingv6.cleverapps.io/developers/changelog/2024-03-11-console-components-update/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;In our ongoing effort to improve our &lt;a href=&#34;https://console.clever-cloud.com&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Console&lt;/a&gt; experience, we upgraded some of its components. It now uses &lt;a href=&#34;https://stagingv6.cleverapps.io/developers/changelog/2024-02-27-js-client-8.2.0/&#34; &gt;JS Client 8.2.0&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://stagingv6.cleverapps.io/developers/changelog/2024-03-07-web-components-v13/&#34; &gt;Web Components 13.0.0&lt;/a&gt;. This update also brings some fixes regarding deployment logs links and Warp10 calls.&lt;/p&gt;

      </description>
